  <num>47-2716</num>
  <heading>Denial of medical or mental health services for inability to pay prohibited.</heading>
  <text>No person shall be denied the services enumerated in §§ <cite path="§47-2713">47-2713</cite> to <cite path="§47-2716">47-2716</cite> because of his or her inability to pay for those services.</text>
